This repository contains a collection of demonstration code written by
Hayden Walles <hayden@hexesandcursors.com> for his blog Hexes and
Cursors <https://hexesandcursors.com>.  Take a look at the blog for
more information.  Code files should contain links to specific posts
where they are discussed.

